# Multilingual Text Summarizer

A FastAPI-based web application that provides both extractive and abstractive text summarization for multiple languages using IndicBART.

## Features
- Multilingual support (Telugu, Hindi, English)
- Extractive summarization using IndicBART embeddings
- Abstractive summarization using IndicBART generation
- BERTScore evaluation for summary quality
- Interactive web interface

## Setup
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```
3. Run the server:
   ```bash
   uvicorn main:app --reload
   ```
4. Access the application at http://localhost:8000

## Usage
- Select language from dropdown
- Choose summarization type (extractive/abstractive)
- Enter text to summarize
- Optionally provide reference summary for evaluation
- Click "Generate Summary" button

## Technical Details
- Backend: FastAPI
- ML Model: IndicBART (ai4bharat/IndicBART)
- Frontend: HTML/CSS/JavaScript
- Evaluation: BERTScore